  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this project is to determine if a 6-session psychotherapy intervention will help
      Veterans feel less deployment-related guilt and less distress related to their guilt. Half of
      the participants will receive the guilt focused intervention and half will receive a
      supportive intervention.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
